Subject: [PATCH] bpf: Use raw_spin_trylock() for pcpu_freelist_push/pop in NMI
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.9.2
Git-commit: 39d8f0d1026a990604770a658708f5845f7dbec0

[ Upstream commit 39d8f0d1026a990604770a658708f5845f7dbec0 ]

